  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's picnic time! Help Pinguino the penguin push tasty treats onto the picnic blanket in this delightful Sokoban-inspired game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/82df8755e9bdef60c62e84924151bfdb.poster.avif?t=1751533260\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/82df8755e9bdef60c62e84924151bfdb.webm?t=1751533260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/82df8755e9bdef60c62e84924151bfdb.mp4?t=1751533260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push multiple blocks at once and rearrange them to clear paths and complete challenging levels. Explore various worlds filled with a wide variety of wacky enemies and puzzles to solve.<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/da72466d7b17d9785c4bc689bba3ae10.webp?t=1751533260\" width=616 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/26fc4704ebce913c41e400eaf8746566.webp?t=1751533260\" width=616 height=32 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Simple and addictive gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Clever puzzles to solve</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple skins </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming 16-bit aesthetics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awesome music</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/e8bc31efe8a9634079274d393c3ac3a8.webp?t=1751533260\" width=616 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/c8af0c7d2921a1658905056af4d4e43b.avif?t=1751533260\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's picnic time! Help Pinguino the penguin push tasty treats onto the picnic blanket in this delightful Sokoban-inspired game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/82df8755e9bdef60c62e84924151bfdb.poster.avif?t=1751533260\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/82df8755e9bdef60c62e84924151bfdb.webm?t=1751533260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/82df8755e9bdef60c62e84924151bfdb.mp4?t=1751533260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push multiple blocks at once and rearrange them to clear paths and complete challenging levels. Explore various worlds filled with a wide variety of wacky enemies and puzzles to solve.<br> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/da72466d7b17d9785c4bc689bba3ae10.webp?t=1751533260\" width=616 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/26fc4704ebce913c41e400eaf8746566.webp?t=1751533260\" width=616 height=32 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Simple and addictive gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Clever puzzles to solve</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple skins </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming 16-bit aesthetics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awesome music</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482240/extras/e8bc31ef